          <![CDATA[ <p><b>York River Wild and Scenic River Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill designates specified segments of the main stem and the tributaries of the York River in Maine as a recreational river.</p> <p>The Department of the Interior may enter into cooperative agreements to provide for the long-term protection, preservation, and enhancement of the river segments. </p> <p>No land or interest in land within the watersheds of the river segments may be acquired by condemnation. </p>]]>
